The paper discusses the challenges and approaches to validating complex autonomous systems operating in open contexts, such as automated driving and mobile robots. This topic falls under the sub-category of Robotics (cs.RO), as well as Software Engineering (cs.SE) and Systems and Control (cs.SY). The paper also discusses the use of algorithms and formalization, which aligns with the sub-category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper touches on the regulatory and safety aspects of these systems, which relates to the sub-category of Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC).
